          "note_text": "FINAL PATHOLOGIC DIAGNOSIS\n\nLeft kidney, partial nephrectomy:\n  - Renal cell carcinoma, clear cell type.\n  - WHO/ISUP nucleolar grade 2 of 4.\n  - Tumor size 3.4 cm, confined to the kidney; margins negative.\n\nIMMUNOHISTOCHEMISTRY\n  CAIX: diffusely positive in tumor cells, supporting clear cell histology.\n  CK7: negative in the tumor.\n  BAP1: nuclear expression retained.\n\nCOMMENT\n  Findings are those of a clear cell renal cell carcinoma. The retained BAP1\n  staining is associated with a more favorable prognostic group."
